text: Harry Bjørnholm was a modern pentathlete from Denmark. Bjørnholm competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics. He was born on 20 July 1891 and died on 20 November 1961.Harry Lorenz Bjørnholm == References == Category:1891 births Category:1961 deaths Category:Modern pentathletes Category:Olympians for Denmark
